  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria (for patients):

          -  Diagnosis of pedophilia

          -  Male

          -  Age between 18 and 65

          -  Informed consent signed

        Inclusion Criteria (for healthy patients):

          -  Male

          -  Age between 18 and 65

          -  Informed consent signed

        Exclusion Criteria (for patients):

          -  IQ &lt;70

          -  Ongoing treatment with cyprostrerone acetate or GnRH agonist or antidepressant
             treatment (5HT reuptake inhibitor)

          -  Ongoing detention

        Exclusion Criteria (for healthy patients):

          -  psychiatric disorders

          -  IQ&lt;70

          -  Sexual disorders
      </textblock>
